name: Capture
description:
Made from vintage 35mm film negatives on glass panel

Hi-res artwork 4000 x 3232 pixels

Original artwork created in 2014 for the 'Memoryscapes' solo show at Absolute Art Gallery in Belgium

The materials used have been contributed by members of the public. A social art project, open to everyone. Find out how to recycle and include your obsolete materials in future artworks by getting in touch.
